title: FIRST NATION GROUP, LLC bags contract for First Nation Group, LLC dba Jordan Reses Supply
body:
United States, Oct. 21 -- United States based FIRST NATION GROUP, LLC has bagged contract from Department 
of Veterans Affairs for First Nation Group, LLC dba Jordan Reses Supply.

The value of the contract is worth $1,529,724,440.00.
